  m_Name: WodeWoDeath
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: KyndeBlade.Core::KyndeBlade.StoryBeat
  BeatId: WodeWoDeath
  Text: "Bleyke hondes recchen fro the glomerynge. The fayerye taken him\u2014noght
    myldeliche. Thei pullen him asondre, rote fro braunche fro breth, as he were nouht.
    His stevene breketh. \"Dremere... I triede my beste... to...\" Cold fyngres shetten.
    What remayneth is scatered. The wode wepeth. He arist noght ayen."
  SpeakerName: Narrator
  Portrait: {fileID: 0}
  DisplayDuration: 10
  WaitForInput: 1
  VisionIndex: 0
  PassusIndex: 0
